The paper focuses on improving the performance of a question answering system using machine learning techniques. This falls under the natural language processing (NLP) domain, which is typically categorized under cs.CL. The paper also uses n-gram based features and neural sentence embeddings, which are commonly used in information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG) research. Additionally, the paper uses gradient boosted regression trees, which is a popular machine learning algorithm used in various domains, including artificial intelligence (AI) and cybernetics (CY).
